    <a href="#%e8%ae%ba%e6%96%872remotesam" class="header-mark"></a>论文2：RemoteSAM</h3><ul>
<li><strong>标题</strong>: RemoteSAM: Towards Segment Anything for Earth Observation</li>
<li><strong>作者</strong>: Liang Yao, Fan Liu et al.</li>
<li><strong>会议</strong>: ACM MM 2025</li>
<li><strong>ArXiv</strong>: 2505.18022</li>
